      • requiresCopy

        boolean requiresCopy(CopyStorageRequest request)
        Test if the copy request is required. In some cases only the meta data needs to be updated when copying or moving files. In other cases, the file data needs to be copied as well.
        Parameters:
        request - the copy request.
        Returns:
        true if this copy request requires copy(CopyStorageRequest) to be called.
